item.title: How do i put my sever on moparscape
item.dc:creator: @loved loved
item.description:
@loved wrote:

[i]Have you downloaded “No-ip”

You need too download “No-ip” and create an account on the website.Then you need too go to “gui.java” in your client and change the IP address to your No-ip address. Your server is online but it is not saying online because your “Gui” is on “127.0.0.1” Having it o n 127.0.0.1 only allows the source hoster too go online. Nobody else could go on your server.

If you would like me too explain it in further detail please tell me what you don’t understand.[/i]
